7. Memory Game: Create a set of vocabulary cards and lay them out face down. Have your child study the cards for a minute or two, then ask them to remember as many as they can recall.
8. Crossword Puzzle: Create a simple crossword puzzle using vocabulary words from the test topic. Help your child fill in the answers.
9. Word Search: Create a word search puzzle using vocabulary words from the test topic. Have your child find and circle each word.
